des:
This is a proof of concept on using walabot radar tracking sleep, a full guide can be seen at https://www.hackster.io/71432/walabot-sleep-quality-tracker-3f168f

Account linking is not needed as the alexa skill shows you how Peter's sleep is, by following the guide using Walabot Radar you can track your own sleep non-invasively.
